front.title: •5D6-RA-7 (Fivedesix)
front.gametext: Power +1 if at same site as Motti or Yularen. Adds 1 to deploy cost of each opponent's droid (and your 'mouse' droids) when deploying to same location. Immune to attrition during 'nighttime conditions.'
front.lore: Aide to Admiral Motti's staff. Foul-tempered and vindictive. Feared by other droids. A spy for the ISB. Secretly investigates Imperial officers whose loyalties are in question.
